the weighted average contractual life remaining for options outstanding and options exercisable at may31, 2012 was 6.3 years and 4.6 years, respectively. the
aggregate intrinsic value for options outstanding and exercisable at may31, 2012 was $1,512 million and $1,008 million, respectively. the aggregate intrinsic value was the amount by which the market value of the underlying stock exceeded the
